Seven years ago,

00:23:33.510 --> 00:23:34.590
Mo Yuanzhi, a doctor,

00:23:34.590 --> 00:23:35.590
announced that he developed

00:23:35.590 --> 00:23:37.650
a new genetic technology called RAN,

00:23:37.720 --> 00:23:40.050
making him his first huge amount
of money.

