Would you like something to drink?

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:12.440
Coffee or tea?

00:24:12.680 --> 00:24:13.550
No, thanks.

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:18.720
Based on your experience,

00:24:19.400 --> 00:24:20.640
when do you think Squid

00:24:20.640 --> 00:24:21.880
will take action?

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:24.240
It's hard to say.

