I also want to ask you.

00:24:26.640 --> 00:24:28.440
From your point of view,

00:24:28.680 --> 00:24:29.590
why do you think Squid

00:24:29.590 --> 00:24:30.750
is targeting Moma?

00:24:33.310 --> 00:24:35.160
The production of our genetic medication

00:24:35.160 --> 00:24:37.790
has greatly affected
traditional pharmaceutical companies.

00:24:37.790 --> 00:24:38.240
Even a few years back,

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:40.370
we'd already made countless enemies.

00:24:40.400 --> 00:24:41.200
And this year,

00:24:41.640 --> 00:24:44.160
we have a project
called RAN-X

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:46.400
that's about to enter
the clinical trial stage.

00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:47.110
Once the experiment succeeds,

00:24:47.110 --> 00:24:48.000
and it enters the market,

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:49.310
this is no exaggeration,

00:24:49.310 --> 00:24:50.550
but at least half
of these companies

00:24:50.550 --> 00:24:51.590
will be affected.

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:54.640
Moma has affected too many people.

00:24:54.920 --> 00:24:55.750
People like Squid

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:57.510
who want to make Moma disappear

00:24:57.790 --> 00:24:58.450
are plenty.

00:25:05.270 --> 00:25:06.330
Please don't mind.

00:25:06.920 --> 00:25:08.780
I'm sorry. This is embarrassing.

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:10.160
I can only

00:25:10.350 --> 00:25:12.010
commemorate them in this way.

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:14.880
After all, according to your requirements,

00:25:14.880 --> 00:25:16.030
I can't attend

00:25:16.030 --> 00:25:17.160
Tang's funeral.

00:25:20.160 --> 00:25:21.110
Of course, I know

00:25:21.110 --> 00:25:22.970
you're doing this for my own good.

00:25:24.270 --> 00:25:24.790
In the building,

00:25:24.790 --> 00:25:27.310
there will be other colleagues of mine
protecting you around the clock.

00:25:27.310 --> 00:25:27.880
But...

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:28.830
let's work together.

00:25:28.830 --> 00:25:30.960
I hope you don't hide anything from us.

00:25:31.030 --> 00:25:32.150
For your safety.

00:25:32.150 --> 00:25:32.750
Okay.

00:25:34.750 --> 00:25:36.610
Let my secretary show you around.

00:25:36.790 --> 00:25:38.200
Can I take a walk by myself?

00:25:38.200 --> 00:25:38.750
Sure.

00:25:39.550 --> 00:25:40.070
Mr. Ding.

00:25:40.070 --> 00:25:41.510
This is the staff pass you requested.

00:25:41.510 --> 00:25:42.440
Okay, thank you.

